# Technology Stack & Design Principles

## Core Frameworks

- Taro.js - Cross-platform mini-program development framework
- React.js - UI development framework
- TailwindCSS - Styling framework

## Key Libraries

- Weapp TailwindCSS - Mini-program TailwindCSS adapter
- Tailwind Variants - Component style variants management

## Design Principles

1. Reference [HeroUI Codebase](mdc:https:/github.com/heroui-inc/heroui) for code style
2. Follow [Adobe React Spectrum](mdc:https:/react-spectrum.adobe.com/react-spectrum/index.html) component design principles
3. Each component should be an independent package

## Component Design Guidelines

1. Keep UI and logic separate
2. Follow presentation/container pattern
3. Use default export for components
4. Manage component styles with tailwind-variants

## Rules

1. Coding with English

